rows.label: qst104206_msg0001
rows.name:
I was really disappointed when
I heard Acedia was gone.

rows.label: qst104206_msg0002
rows.name:
I was just getting ready to go
to the theological school...

rows.label: qst104206_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll help out a lot! I'll
even carry the heavy stuff!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0101
rows.name:
Did you bring some wood?
I'll take anything!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0121
rows.name:
We still need more wood.
Bring as much as you can!

rows.label: qst104206_msg0201
rows.name:
I was sad I couldn't go to the
theological school, but...

rows.label: qst104206_msg0202
rows.name:
...building a school here is
definitely going to be more fun.

rows.label: qst104206_msg0251
rows.name:
Hummer-san can make anything out
of any material! He's amazing...
